ricEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":34,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Sir Ralph Ashton was born in 1421, in Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England. He had at least 1 daughter. He died in 1486, in his hometown, at the age of 65."},"et":{"1421–1486":"1421–1486","1430–1485":"1430–1485","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1486":"1486","1485":"1485","1430":"1430","Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England"},"fi":{"1421–1486":"1421–1486","1430–1485":"1430–1485","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1486":"1486","1485":"1485","1430":"1430","Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England"},"fr":{"1421–1486":"1421–1486","1430–1485":"1430–1485","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1486":"1486","1485":"1485","1430":"1430","Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Sir Ralph Ashton est né en 1421, à Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, Angleterre. Il a eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé en 1486, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 65 ans."},"de":{"1421–1486":"1421–1486","1430–1485":"1430–1485","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1486":"1486","1485":"1485","1430":"1430","Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England":"Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England","lifeSummary":"Sir Ralph Ashton wurde 1421 in Ashton-under-Lyne, Lancashire, England geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Tochter. Er starb 1486 im Alter von 65 Jahren in seinem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1421–1486":"1421–1486","1430–1485":"1430–1485","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","1